EmailTemplate.subject: FET 2017 OCR & EDO is Now Live!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Receiving_User.FirstName},
Freestyle Announcement! All OCR & EDO deployment activities are now complete and all scheduled changes and enhancements are now live.
You can now resume all normal activities. Although we have performed exhaustive testing; if you experience any issues please report them to your manager so they can address them via FET Help.
Attached you will find a set of release notes, which describe some of the changes included with this release.
As always thank you for your continued support!
FET Support Team | E-mail: FETHelp@coca-cola.com
